&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About RTW Investments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RTW Investments, LP (&quot;RTW&quot;) is a global, full-life cycle investment and innovation firm dedicated to solving the most challenging, unmet patient needs. We are focused on building companies and identifying transformative and disruptive innovations across the biopharmaceutical and medical technology sectors. Our investment philosophy combines deep understanding of disease, biology, medicine, and technology with a comprehensive view of commercial opportunities and challenges. Backed by a team with hands-on experience in key areas of innovation, we support emerging breakthroughs across both industry and academia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission is simple: we power breakthrough therapies that transform the lives of millions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rtwfunds.com/news-events/news/&quot;&gt;RTW Investments – Recent Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RTW Investments is seeking a Management Company Controller to join its Firm Services team. This senior accounting role has broad responsibility for the firm’s management company financial operations, including accounts payable, expense management, internal controls, month-end close, financial reporting, and oversight of the annual audit. The ideal candidate is a seasoned accounting professional who can independently lead the function, build strong relationships with internal stakeholders and outsourced providers, and bring structure and reliability to RTW’s management company operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This person will serve as RTW’s primary internal contact for the outsourced accounting service provider, ensuring accurate financial reporting, adherence to firm processes and controls as well as the smooth execution of payment processing and reimbursements. At its core, the role is about ownership: the person in this seat is expected to lead the function with accountability and to approach every RTW colleague with a strong client-service mindset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to the Managing Director of Finance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Key Responsibilities &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
