&lt;li&gt;Oversee the monthly financial close for the management company, including account reconciliations, management company financial statements, and timely delivery to senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish, document, and enforce internal controls and financial policies; ensure the control environment keeps pace with firm growth and evolving regulatory expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent RTW in key vendor and counterparty relationships with professionalism and authority.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversight of annual audits for RTW’s global management company entities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner directly with RTW’s internal tax team to address requests and support ongoing needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Longer term goal to assist with annual budgeting, ongoing variance analysis, and management reporting for the management company; surface insights, identify and proactively resolve issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
