&lt;p&gt;RTW Investments is seeking a Private Wealth Analyst / Internal Sales Specialist whose primary responsibilities would be building and managing advisor relationships across wirehouses, private banks, and RIA networks. This is a proactive, inside sales role for a self-starter who owns their coverage universe end-to-end reaching out to advisors ahead of roadshows, managing the pipeline, logging every interaction, and following up with urgency and precision. Some familiarity with alternative investments is helpful; the ability to build trust with busy financial advisors and operate with high organizational discipline is essential. This role is a unique opportunity to help shape RTW’s private wealth distribution channel from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
