&lt;li&gt;Approximately 2–4 years of experience in financial services, with exposure to the wealth management or alternatives distribution ecosystem (wirehouse, prime brokerage, hedge fund IR, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with alternative investments, hedge fund structures, and the broader wealth management industry; deep investment experience is not required, but intellectual curiosity about the strategies being sold is expected&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to build trust and long-term partnerships with busy wealth advisors and private bankers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial and self-directed, high energy, meticulous attention to detail, follow-through, organizational discipline, and the ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
